      "name": "Brown Digital Repository (BDR)",
      "url": "https://repository.library.brown.edu",
      "description": "Platform for gathering, indexing, storing, preserving, and making available digital assets from scholarly, instructional, research, and administrative activity at Brown. Exposes a public REST/Solr search API returning DigitalDocument and CreativeWork objects, plus a IIIF image and presentation service."
